Comment: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:07.97,Sakakura Sakura,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Opening Skit ===
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:07.97,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Mei-chan, you've really become reliable lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.97,0:00:08.84,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.84,0:00:12.42,Yabushima Akane,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"It seems my sister trusts Mei-senpai quite a lot too."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.42,0:00:13.80,3,host,0,0,0,,N-Natsumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.48,0:00:16.58,3,host,0,0,0,,It really doesn't look that way, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.58,0:00:17.68,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.68,0:00:21.18,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I feel like Mei-chan naturally leads the first and second years
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.18,0:00:23.20,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,and pushes them forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.88,0:00:27.96,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Just as Kanon-senpai says, Mei-senpai takes the initiative to keep everyone together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.04,0:00:30.68,3,host,0,0,0,,Well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.76,0:00:35.06,3,host,0,0,0,,If I don't do it, everyone just does whatever they want,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.06,0:00:36.08,3,host,0,0,0,,so I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:39.92,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It's impressive that you can step up without hesitating.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.44,0:00:44.24,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,If it were me, I'd just leave the leadership to Chi-chan or Ren-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.00,0:00:49.90,Yabushima Akane,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Mei-senpai was very reliable when we headed to the Music World as well."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.90,0:00:52.14,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Oh, I heard about that from Margarete-chan."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.14,0:00:53.72,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,You did great, Mei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.72,0:00:58.56,3,host,0,0,0,,At the time, I just wanted to be a bit more like Chisato-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.23,0:00:59.73,3,host,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.40,0:01:04.66,3,host,0,0,0,,looking back, I think I was trying a bit too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.66,0:01:06.08,Yabushima Akane,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I think that's fine."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.76,0:01:11.83,Yabushima Akane,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Mei-senpai working hard has the benefit of making Liella more positive."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.83,0:01:12.57,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I totally get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.16,0:01:15.24,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It makes us feel like we can't afford to lose either.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.93,0:01:16.43,3,host,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.24,0:01:18.48,3,host,0,0,0,,Kanon-senpai and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.84,0:01:20.88,3,host,0,0,0,,No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.88,0:01:24.20,3,host,0,0,0,,There's no way you seniors would lose to someone like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.20,0:01:25.86,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Don't say that, Mei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.86,0:01:28.08,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,You just said "someone like me," didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.76,0:01:33.08,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,You have more power to move those around you than you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.72,0:01:36.48,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,And the kindness to support others, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.48,0:01:37.41,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.41,0:01:39.44,Yabushima Akane,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Margarete says it often too."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.04,0:01:42.37,Yabushima Akane,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I can't afford to lose to Mei-senpai,"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:43.01,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.96,0:01:45.84,3,host,0,0,0,,I can definitely imagine her saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.04,0:01:50.42,3,host,0,0,0,,Still, your Margarete impression is spot on, Tomari.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.42,0:01:51.56,Yabushima Akane,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I'm honored."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.56,0:01:54.96,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Anyway, Mei-chan, you're the driving force of Liella,"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.96,0:01:56.36,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,so I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.44,0:01:58.52,3,host,0,0,0,,Driving force?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.08,0:02:02.36,3,host,0,0,0,,Well, that might be a bit much...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.16,0:02:07.20,3,host,0,0,0,,But fine, I'm always ready to jump-start the engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.20,0:02:08.88,Yabushima Akane,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"How reliable."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:15.38,Yabushima Akane,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Then please, go ahead and fire up my sister's motivation for the next exams."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.38,0:02:16.07,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.07,0:02:16.69,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,that's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.36,0:02:19.76,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Then, fire up my passion for baking sweets too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.48,0:02:22.60,3,host,0,0,0,,Don't get carried away, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:25.28,3,host,0,0,0,,I can't look after you that much!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.00,0:02:43.12,4,host,0,0,0,,Love Live! Superstar!! Yuigaoka Girls' High School Broadcasting Club: Lieraji! Kanon, Tomari, and Mei.
Comment: 0,0:02:49.79,0:02:50.29,Date Sayuri,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Self-Introductions ===
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.79,0:02:50.29,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Hello,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.16,0:02:52.12,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.64,0:02:54.64,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I'm Date Sayuri, the voice of Kanon Shibuya."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.64,0:02:57.28,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I'm Sakakura Sakura, also known as Saku-chan, the voice of Tomari Onitsuka."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:02:58.96,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,And I'm Yabushima Akane, also known as Yabu-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:03:00.62,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"the voice of Mei Yoneme."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.62,0:03:01.44,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,We are...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.04,0:03:03.24,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Liella!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:05.08,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"It's great to be here!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.93,0:03:06.43,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.24,0:03:10.68,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"So today, we're bringing you the Tomo-Kano-Mei trio."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.68,0:03:11.18,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Mei-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.76,0:03:12.76,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Let's do this!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:13.64,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.85,0:03:15.35,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Happy to be here!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.07,0:03:16.57,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thanks for having me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:25.24,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Today is March 24th, but coming up on March 28th, which is Sunny Pa Day..."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.24,0:03:30.30,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"It's the birthday of Yoshitake-chan, who plays Yuna Hijirisawa!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:31.20,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.20,0:03:32.36,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Happy birthday!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.36,0:03:34.58,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Sunny Pa Day really is Sunny Pa Day!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.58,0:03:35.90,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It's destiny, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:37.13,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.13,0:03:37.75,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Isn't it great?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:39.28,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It really is. Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:41.16,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Let's all celebrate on the day!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.16,0:03:42.37,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Please do!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.37,0:03:42.93,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"We're counting on you!"
Comment: 0,0:03:43.48,0:03:46.60,Sakakura Sakura,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Suggestion Box ===
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.48,0:03:46.60,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"And so, we've received some mail."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.60,0:03:47.64,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.40,0:03:50.28,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"It's from Liella name: Kabo-san."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.28,0:03:51.36,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you so much."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.36,0:03:52.16,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.72,0:03:55.61,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Congratulations on being confirmed for Lucky Fes!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.61,0:03:56.17,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.48,0:04:05.08,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It's been one of my dreams to see Liella perform in Ibaraki, which is both my hometown and the hometown of the Onitsuka sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:12.56,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"When I saw the announcement that you'd be performing there, I almost screamed out loud at work because I was so overwhelmed with emotion."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:13.13,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.13,0:04:17.80,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,The venue, Hitachi Seaside Park, is a place where I went on field trips as a kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.80,0:04:22.74,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,and I have so many memories of having barbecues there with my family and friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.74,0:04:27.08,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"So I'm really happy that I'll get to make new memories there with everyone in Liella."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.08,0:04:27.63,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:32.96,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I'm looking forward to having an amazing time with Liella again this summer."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:33.68,Sakakura Sakura,host_meta,0,0,0,,That's what they wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.68,0:04:34.56,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you so much."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.56,0:04:35.88,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.72,0:04:40.58,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Next is from Liella name: Takashi from Sendai. Thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.58,0:04:41.92,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:44.36,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Congratulations on your appearance at LuckyFes."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:45.27,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.92,0:04:48.74,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Since the festival is in Ibaraki, a place you have a special connection to,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.74,0:04:50.39,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I think it feels extra special."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:51.00,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:57.08,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Since it's a summer festival, please sweep the venue up in a whirlwind of excitement with Liella's hot performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:04:57.63,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.63,0:05:01.44,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I'm also excited to see if you'll perform any classic summer songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:02.42,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,True. Oh, and they asked, "If you have any goals for the festival
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:09.70,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,or things you want to try at a summer festival, please let us know!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:10.90,Sakakura Sakura,host_meta,0,0,0,,That's what they sent in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.90,0:05:11.74,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you so much."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:12.76,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.40,0:05:17.80,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Yes, Liella will be performing on Day 2 of LuckyFes, on the 9th."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:20.40,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"It's officially been decided!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:21.16,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,We're performing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.12,0:05:23.58,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.58,0:05:24.80,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:25.44,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I'm so happy."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.44,0:05:26.20,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:28.04,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It's so great that it's in Ibaraki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:28.60,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.60,0:05:30.22,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It's so exciting.
Comment: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:33.92,Date Sayuri,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Self-Introductions ===
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:33.92,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Since it's the Onitsuka sisters' hometown,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.92,0:05:37.32,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,we've always wanted to perform in Ibaraki someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:42.92,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I'm so happy it's coming true! And the other artists are just...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:44.19,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:44.86,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:45.52,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It's a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.52,0:05:46.89,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I was really surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.89,0:05:47.56,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.56,0:05:51.88,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"We'll do our best to show off Liella's power and keep up with them!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.88,0:05:52.49,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:53.50,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"We're counting on your support."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:54.20,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Please support us!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:55.24,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It'll be midsummer, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.24,0:05:56.88,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,August 8th and 9th.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:05:59.00,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Uh, make sure to stay nourished...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:05:59.97,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,and come see us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.97,0:06:00.84,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:02.23,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Bring sports drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:02.77,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Bring sports drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.32,0:06:04.96,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Are we gonna perform while holding sports drinks?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:05.95,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Well, should we?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.95,0:06:07.04,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,They might spray everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.04,0:06:07.94,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Spray everywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.94,0:06:08.59,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,That's bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.48,0:06:10.26,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,So sticky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.26,0:06:11.66,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,We'd be all sticky!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:12.66,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Even though it's a festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.66,0:06:13.56,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Even though it's a festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:14.06,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It's way too hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.72,0:06:17.78,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Everyone, please come and see us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.78,0:06:19.84,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"We're looking forward to it!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.84,0:06:22.62,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Well then, everyone, please stay with us until the end!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.62,0:06:28.60,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Love Live! Superstar!! Yuigaoka Broadcasting Station, Liella! Let's Super Start!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:35.48,4,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Love Live! Superstar!! Yuigaoka Broadcasting Station, Liella!"
Comment: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:44.50,Sakakura Sakura,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Suggestion Box ===
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:44.50,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"It's time for the Yuigaoka Girls' High School Suggestion Box, where we read your letters."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:48.36,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Alright, everyone, let's say it together! One, two... Suggestion Box!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.12,0:06:50.88,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Okay, let's introduce some mail."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:53.48,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,This one is from Liella name: Miku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.48,0:06:54.58,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:55.72,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you very much."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:07:01.92,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I attended both days of the 7th Live in Kanagawa and watched the Aichi performance via stream."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.92,0:07:07.45,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Mei-chan's solo song, "Sky Linker," started with her taking the baton from the club president, Chisato-chan."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.45,0:07:08.06,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.06,0:07:12.48,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"What was especially memorable was when she thrust her fist forward at the end of the chorus."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.48,0:07:13.15,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I totally get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.15,0:07:18.18,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Since it happened several times during the song, I was moved to tears the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.18,0:07:20.80,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"and from the second time on, I was thrusting my fist along with her."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.80,0:07:21.43,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.43,0:07:24.54,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It was a performance where I felt the full extent of Mei-chan's straightforward strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:29.76,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"encompassing her great love, her kindness that embraces weakness, and her desire to protect."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:30.64,Sakakura Sakura,host_meta,0,0,0,,That's what they wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.64,0:07:31.78,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.78,0:07:33.04,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you so much."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.04,0:07:36.36,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Next is from Liella name: Baron Ojipan."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.36,0:07:37.46,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.46,0:07:38.44,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you very much."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.96,0:07:43.94,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Regarding "Sky Linker," the clapping with hands near the face during the instrumental break,"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:47.60,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"and the side steps after that, looked like a traditional Spanish dance—"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.60,0:07:49.20,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"flamenco."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.20,0:07:49.77,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.77,0:07:52.80,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Spain is often called the land of passion,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:57.40,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,and I felt that Mei-chan's hidden inner passion was being expressed through the dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.40,0:08:00.52,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,The moment I first saw it, I thought, "Whoa, that's so cool!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.52,0:08:01.56,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"That's how it felt to me."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:03.66,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,And with that, ciao.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.66,0:08:05.68,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"That's a parting greeting in Spanish."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.68,0:08:06.80,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,(Laughs) That's what they said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.80,0:08:07.74,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.74,0:08:08.72,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you very much."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.72,0:08:09.34,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Ciao!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:09.84,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Ciao!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:14.36,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Okay, next is from Liella name: Red-haired Kana. Thank you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:15.68,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:20.60,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Seeing "Sky Linker" on Day 1 of the 7th Live in Kanagawa was truly the best."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:24.10,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah. Yabu-chan's dance was so cool I couldn't get it out of my head,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:25.64,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"and it still leaves a strong impression on me."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.16,0:08:28.42,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"The song and lyrics are great, so I listen to it all the time."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:31.83,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I'd love to see the "Sky Linker" dance again somewhere!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.83,0:08:32.84,Sakakura Sakura,host_meta,0,0,0,,That's what they sent in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:33.98,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.98,0:08:35.65,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you very much."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:36.21,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:39.00,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I want to hear all about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:41.40,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,"Sky Linker" was so incredibly cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.40,0:08:41.90,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.44,0:08:52.30,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,At first, I thought she might perform with a mic stand or just stand there and hype up the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.30,0:08:52.90,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:56.14,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I couldn't really imagine her doing an intense dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.14,0:08:56.90,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.90,0:09:02.92,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I kept wondering how it would turn out, but I never expected flamenco in the instrumental break.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.92,0:09:03.42,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.40,0:09:08.70,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Well, it was a really valuable experience for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.70,0:09:10.69,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I don't think I'll ever get another chance to do flamenco.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.69,0:09:11.46,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.46,0:09:16.54,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,When I first saw the video of Mei-chan's choreography,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.54,0:09:18.40,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I was like, "What kind of dance is this?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.40,0:09:22.64,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It was a style none of us had ever done before,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:29.58,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,so when I said, "This is amazing," and heard it was flamenco, I was shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.58,0:09:33.28,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I was like, "How do you even do that?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:32.70,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.64,0:09:34.74,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I couldn't do it at all at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.74,0:09:36.12,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.12,0:09:42.84,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It used core muscles I'd never used before, and the whole foundation of the dance
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.84,0:09:47.96,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,was just completely different. I don't know much about dance myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.96,0:09:50.44,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,but even so, it was so difficult I didn't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:50.94,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:56.86,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I practiced that instrumental part over and over at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:09:57.58,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.58,0:09:59.00,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,But you were really good at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.00,0:10:00.46,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It looked so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.46,0:10:01.44,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It makes me nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.44,0:10:03.08,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:08.00,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Since we all do our choreography lessons for our solos individually,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:12.02,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,we don't even know when the others are practicing, or even...
Comment: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:17.12,Date Sayuri,,0,0,0,chunk_debug,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:17.12,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,We didn't really know if each other's songs would have dancing or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.68,0:10:21.08,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,So when I met the other members, I'd ask things like,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.08,0:10:22.96,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,"Wait, does Kanon's song have dancing?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.96,0:10:24.32,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,or "How much dancing is there?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:26.76,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,We had conversations like that all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:32.98,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I happened to run into Yabu right after she finished her choreography lesson for Mei's song,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:38.88,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,and she muttered something like, "It turned out to be flamenco..."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.88,0:10:42.18,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,And I was like, "Wait, what do you mean?" I was so confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.18,0:10:44.80,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I couldn't wrap my head around the word "flamenco."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.48,0:10:48.32,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Like Yabu said earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.32,0:10:52.36,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I thought she'd be standing firm at a mic stand,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:57.36,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,with a burning intensity, but then I heard "flamenco."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.36,0:11:02.80,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,You don't really get many chances to see flamenco, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:03.88,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Liella probably wouldn't do it normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.88,0:11:04.38,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,No, we wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.92,0:11:06.28,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,All of us doing flamenco together?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.91,0:11:07.54,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Probably not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.54,0:11:12.40,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It must be hard when you don't know what the "right" way looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:18.77,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Even just watching it looks difficult, so doing it yourself must have been a huge challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.77,0:11:19.38,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It's really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.38,0:11:23.00,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,But I saw how much you practiced.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.00,0:11:24.32,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, your moves were so sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.32,0:11:25.95,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It was incredibly cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:26.62,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:34.60,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Like Miku-san said, that part where you thrust your fist forward felt so direct and very Mei-like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.76,0:11:31.26,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.72,0:11:35.56,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, I totally get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.12,0:11:42.36,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It didn't even feel like choreography anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.36,0:11:40.86,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.44,0:11:43.10,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:47.96,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It felt like you were punching out of pure emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:54.68,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I got really swept up in the feeling too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.24,0:11:53.74,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:11:58.56,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,That's at the end of the song... well, the first part...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.56,0:11:59.52,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,The end of the second verse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.52,0:12:03.60,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,And I do it in the final chorus and at the very end too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:08.68,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,The movement is the same every time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.68,0:12:13.72,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,but I felt like the emotion behind it was different in the first, second, and final parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.72,0:12:20.16,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Depending on the performance, what I'm feeling in that moment changes,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.72,0:12:23.40,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,so I put all those feelings into my fist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.40,0:12:24.12,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:25.68,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:26.51,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.51,0:12:28.70,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I really love the sound of the glass breaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.70,0:12:29.23,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.00,0:12:31.24,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,That part is so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.24,0:12:31.97,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.97,0:12:35.48,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,You can hear it even better during the live show.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.84,0:12:34.34,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Totally.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.68,0:12:40.28,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It really resonated, and the flames in the background...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:43.56,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,matched Mei so well, it was awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.68,0:12:42.18,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.96,0:12:47.68,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Actually, right after that, we had to get ready for "Fantastic Departure!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:48.00,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:48.61,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.61,0:12:53.32,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,So I was watching Mei's performance from the side while preparing,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.32,0:12:57.12,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,and feeling that heat, the two of us were like, "Alright, let's go!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.12,0:12:59.04,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,"Let's keep this momentum going!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:02.42,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"It was really, really good."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.42,0:13:03.34,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"You were so cool."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:04.28,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you so much."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.28,0:13:11.60,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Can I say something too? Since Kanon performs before Mei,"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:14.66,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"there's a bit of time before my next turn."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.66,0:13:19.28,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"During that time, I was able to watch Mei right before she went on to sing."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.28,0:13:21.00,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"From the wings."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:24.72,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"And of course, before that too,"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.72,0:13:31.92,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"but there were times I'd see Yabu right after her performance ended."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.92,0:13:38.86,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Even though she had that passionate, "I gave it my all" look,"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.86,0:13:42.96,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"she always had this expression like she was already thinking..."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:47.28,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,"What should I do next?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:47.78,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,That's how Yabu looked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:51.80,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,So, how do I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.80,0:13:56.04,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,She had a sense of accomplishment in her own way,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.64,0:14:00.48,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,but she also looked like she was thinking, "I'm not there yet."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:01.20,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Backstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:04.56,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,That just looked so much like Mei to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.44,0:14:08.72,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I was about to cry while drinking my hot water.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.72,0:14:09.22,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Me."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:11.56,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"It was so Mei!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:16.36,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"We were all thinking, "It was already so amazing!""
Comment: 0,0:14:16.36,0:14:17.72,Date Sayuri,,0,0,0,chunk_debug,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.36,0:14:17.72,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Everyone feels that way, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.32,0:14:20.20,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Like, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.20,0:14:21.04,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Your own what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:24.76,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,That the wall is so high... no, no, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:25.76,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Everyone's like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:32.08,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Everyone has such high aspirations and shares that mindset.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:38.12,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,That's why I'm inspired to work harder myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.12,0:14:41.88,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,If it were just me, I might not have felt that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:47.12,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,But seeing and feeling everyone's performance made me think I could go further.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.12,0:14:51.44,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I think I felt like there was more I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.44,0:14:53.30,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah. Wow, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.30,0:14:57.52,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,We really did inspire each other with the solo songs this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.52,0:15:00.20,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I felt that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:14:59.54,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Mutual inspiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.40,0:15:02.68,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I was really happy about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.68,0:15:03.57,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Supporting each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:04.16,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.16,0:15:11.48,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Even though they're solo songs, I felt like I wasn't alone during those performances.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.48,0:15:14.70,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It felt like we were all building them together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.70,0:15:16.22,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Oh, and the costumes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:17.92,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,That 'Girl Crush' style.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.92,0:15:19.74,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It's so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.74,0:15:21.82,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I've never worn anything like that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.82,0:15:23.22,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,So cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.22,0:15:28.36,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I think it's the closest to everyday clothes, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:29.04,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.04,0:15:33.51,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It wouldn't look out of place if you were walking through a stylish city.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.51,0:15:34.14,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.14,0:15:36.20,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, some people probably wear stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:36.70,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:39.04,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"The fishnet tights were lovely."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:41.38,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"It was the first time in my life wearing them."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.38,0:15:42.28,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Fishnet tights, of all things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:44.64,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Is it okay for everyone to see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.64,0:15:47.28,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I'm just full of gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:47.83,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.83,0:15:49.12,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,We were practically worshipping you backstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.12,0:15:50.19,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I definitely was.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.19,0:15:50.76,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I saw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:53.40,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Oh, and during the finale—or maybe just a late show—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.00,0:15:59.16,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,it wasn't part of the choreo, but her hair got in her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.16,0:16:04.34,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Kanon brushed it away while looking forward or down...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.34,0:16:07.88,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I forget which, but she did this hair-flip motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.88,0:16:10.77,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,And the camera caught it perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.77,0:16:11.38,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,That's so embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.38,0:16:14.44,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It was just too good. Like, wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.44,0:16:16.12,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I'd definitely keep rewatching that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.84,0:16:17.72,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It was the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.28,0:16:19.92,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Thank you, hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.92,0:16:21.44,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It was seriously so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.44,0:16:23.16,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I was just like, 'Whoa!'
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.16,0:16:23.87,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,So cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.43,0:16:25.04,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:26.92,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yabu-san doesn't even remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:28.02,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,She really doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:30.60,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,But it was so beautiful, I loved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.75,0:16:32.30,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I loved it."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:32.85,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:34.24,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Gosh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.24,0:16:34.74,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:37.42,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Everyone, please check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.42,0:16:38.64,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yes, please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:39.44,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Please watch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.44,0:16:40.44,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Maybe someone's already mentioned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.44,0:16:41.64,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Please remember that moment, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.08,0:16:44.10,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you so much."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:45.38,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:49.32,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Moving on, this next one is from Liella name: Hajiketa Kata Popcorn."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:50.46,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.46,0:16:51.58,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you so much."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.58,0:16:53.92,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Love Live! Superstar!! Liella! 7th Live."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.00,0:18:02.30,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,That was tough, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.30,0:18:03.12,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It really was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:09.86,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,All the 2nd and 3rd years were saying this,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.86,0:18:18.16,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,but the choreography was incredibly difficult. And it's the kind of difficulty
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:24.76,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,that's hard for the audience to imagine. From the outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.76,0:18:29.52,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,it looks like we're having fun and dancing effortlessly, but honestly,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.52,0:18:31.38,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,it was so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.38,0:18:32.70,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It really was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.70,0:18:34.98,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Yeah, it was truly a struggle."
Comment: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:40.56,Sakakura Sakura,,0,0,0,chunk_debug,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:40.56,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Yeah, when we first learned the choreo, I think everyone's soul almost left their body."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.52,0:19:05.50,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"We were all so worried about whether we could actually dance while singing because it was so intense. But the more we practiced, the more we got in sync, and eventually, that anxiety turned into excitement during the performance."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.50,0:19:19.88,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"So on the day of the live, instead of being overcome with worry, I felt like I could really enjoy that sense of unity with the audience. What did you guys think?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:18.92,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.28,0:19:24.88,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Right. Ever since 'High Motivation' was announced...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.88,0:19:35.96,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,...so many people were saying how much they were looking forward to seeing the performance, which felt like a lot of pressure. But honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.96,0:19:44.76,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,...I also thought the choreography would be a bit simpler or 'sweeter,' you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.76,0:19:44.26,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I thought so too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.76,0:19:45.96,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,But there's actually a lot of dancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:49.36,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Wait, why is it like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.32,0:19:50.84,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.52,0:20:07.68,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I was worried we wouldn't be able to express the fun of the song properly. But as the live got closer, all that practice turned into confidence. By the day of, I just wanted to have fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:19:57.50,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.84,0:20:18.28,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,...and make sure the audience had fun too. I wanted to show everyone the power that just the 2nd and 3rd gen members have.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.92,0:20:09.48,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.28,0:20:31.92,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Well, we managed to have fun in the end, but at first, I couldn't even think about that. I was just desperate. The first time we tried singing and dancing at the same time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.28,0:20:28.78,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.92,0:20:37.62,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,...we were all like, 'This is impossible! There's no way!'
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.62,0:20:48.60,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Even though there were fewer of us than the full eleven, we couldn't even find a place to breathe. The formations were so difficult too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:55.84,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,And the way the rhythm is caught... it's not just a simple one-two-three-four.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.84,0:21:03.48,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,The choreographer had us hitting such tiny, intricate beats with the dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.60,0:21:06.66,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It really was something, but it turned out great.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:07.40,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, it did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.40,0:21:11.00,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,So, what part was especially difficult?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:17.80,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,From our perspective watching you, it looked like you were hitting every single beat, like Saku just said.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.80,0:21:24.60,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,But since we weren't the ones dancing, we just ended up thinking, 'Wow, that looks like fun!'
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.19,0:21:25.74,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.74,0:21:27.12,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,So, which part was the hardest?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.12,0:21:30.86,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,With other songs, I can usually point to one specific part that was tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.86,0:21:38.12,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,But with this one, every single part is a little bit difficult, so it felt like it was hard the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.52,0:21:36.04,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.21,0:21:38.93,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, totally.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.93,0:21:40.44,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It's just... tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.44,0:21:46.68,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,How should I put it? Usually, when it's not your turn to sing, you might just be standing there watching the others...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.68,0:21:49.44,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,...but there are almost no scenes like that in this song.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.44,0:21:50.98,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,You're always doing one or the other, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.98,0:22:00.96,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,We're constantly moving, and while the formations were hard, it was mostly just being out of breath from non-stop movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.64,0:21:58.32,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.95,0:22:01.45,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.64,0:22:07.12,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I can say this now, but I was a mess when we were learning the choreo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.01,0:22:08.51,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.25,0:22:09.85,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,You were?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.85,0:22:12.95,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I mean, we were all doing it while crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.95,0:22:13.62,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.62,0:22:15.36,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I was just sobbing the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.36,0:22:17.76,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Man, I really wondered what was going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.56,0:22:19.40,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,How did it get to that point?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.40,0:22:23.80,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I kept thinking, 'Mei-chan would never cry...'
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.36,0:22:20.92,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.80,0:22:28.72,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,...so seeing her like that made me cry even more. I don't even know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.20,0:22:26.12,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,No, no, that's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.21,0:22:27.71,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Ahaha.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.40,0:22:30.60,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Well, I can talk about it now that it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.36,0:22:43.08,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Everyone probably practiced a ton at home, because every time we met up again, the quality had improved so much. I was really impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.88,0:22:46.96,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Wait, isn't there a line in the lyrics about 'having changed'?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.76,0:22:51.82,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Hearing that story now makes me think that's exactly what it was about.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.82,0:22:54.86,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I wasn't in it since I'm a 1st gen member, but..."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.86,0:22:58.08,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"...the song title is 'High Motivation,' right?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.29,0:22:59.79,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.32,0:23:04.24,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Even during rehearsals, the 2nd and 3rd gen members would shout, 'Alright!'
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.24,0:23:08.44,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,'High motivation!' to pump themselves up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.08,0:23:12.16,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Seeing that just made me think, 'Wow, they're so cool.'
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.28,0:23:18.20,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, because you really can't get through a song like that without that kind of motivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.76,0:23:22.58,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,But during the actual performance, everyone looked so happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.58,0:23:30.56,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,...and you were all smiling, so I realized just how much hard work must have gone into getting to that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.72,0:23:29.96,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Everyone worked so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.88,0:23:31.66,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Because everyone gave it their all...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.66,0:23:32.40,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,...it turned out great.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.72,0:23:35.50,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,By the way, did you see Nako's impression?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.50,0:23:36.61,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Wait, what impression?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.61,0:23:37.12,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Oh, you haven't seen it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.12,0:23:38.55,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,You should definitely have her show you sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.55,0:23:39.12,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,What is it? Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.12,0:23:39.80,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Did you take a video?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.80,0:23:43.48,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,No, I didn't, but she's always mimicking the choreography for 'High Motivation'...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.48,0:23:49.14,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,...and it's so cute, so you should really ask Nako to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.14,0:23:49.80,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I want to see it! I want to see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.80,0:23:52.12,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,She mimics a very specific part.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.12,0:23:52.82,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.82,0:23:53.47,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Man, I've gotta see that.
Comment: 0,0:23:55.40,0:23:56.60,Date Sayuri,,0,0,0,chunk_debug,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.40,0:23:56.60,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Wait, what is it? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.60,0:23:57.86,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you so much."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.86,0:23:58.64,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.64,0:23:59.40,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Wow, that's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.16,0:24:03.42,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Alright, we've talked a lot today,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.42,0:24:06.68,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"but we still haven't said enough, so we'll continue next week."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.68,0:24:07.18,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.68,0:24:10.90,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Anyway, thank you all so much for all your mail."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.90,0:24:11.56,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you!"
Comment: 0,0:24:12.16,0:24:15.47,Date Sayuri,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Lunchtime Request ===
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.16,0:24:15.47,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Now, let's read a message for Lunchtime Request."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.47,0:24:16.08,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.08,0:24:18.88,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"It's from Liella name: Mizuki."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.88,0:24:19.96,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.96,0:24:21.10,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you very much."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.10,0:24:23.28,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I'd like to request 'Sky Linker'."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.28,0:24:28.50,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"My favorite part of this song is definitely right before the final chorus,"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.50,0:24:30.86,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"specifically the 'I'll change it right now' part."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.86,0:24:35.98,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Mei-chan usually has a lower voice, but here she hits such a clear high note."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.98,0:24:40.72,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I love the gap and how her singing sounds like a cry from the soul."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.72,0:24:42.12,Date Sayuri,host_meta,0,0,0,,Thanks for writing in.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.96,0:24:43.80,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.72,0:24:46.16,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,You can really feel the soul in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.80,0:24:59.92,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"It's a very passionate song, so I hope you'll listen closely to the vocals and the music in the background."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.92,0:25:01.82,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Please listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.82,0:25:03.88,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Mei Yoneme, 'Sky Linker'.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.16,0:25:10.52,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,You're only noticing the missing pieces
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.32,0:25:18.48,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,because you know what the perfect shape looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.72,0:25:21.28,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,And that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.44,0:25:28.28,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,No need for a period on someone's hesitation; I'm far from being a god,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.80,0:25:36.40,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,but I'll get drenched with you until we find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.68,0:25:42.36,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,My wish is in the blue sky; I'll take the hand that reaches for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.08,0:25:47.74,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,I'll block out everything, yes, everything that gets in our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.74,0:25:50.68,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,I'll even protect you from fate itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.17,0:25:52.67,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Always,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.24,0:25:58.60,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,yes, always, don't lose to a world turning gloomy, not today.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.60,0:26:00.24,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Rise up
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.96,0:26:14.20,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,through the many... Fly and leap over to our destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.76,0:26:18.28,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,We've become what they call 'comrades'.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.96,0:26:29.20,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,When I pray for someone other than myself, I'll prove there's not a single cloud of doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.04,0:26:35.72,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Dive into the blue sky; if you'll take my hand, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.29,0:26:37.79,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.36,0:26:40.72,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,yes, everything—what's wrong with being weak?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.24,0:26:44.16,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,If you want to cry, let's wail together; I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.47,0:26:46.18,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Always,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.18,0:26:50.20,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,yes, always, I'll accept any version of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.96,0:26:51.88,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Just show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.12,0:27:20.92,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Even if you're cracked, I'll catch it all and show you I won't break.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.52,0:27:32.24,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,If you want a tough vessel or a clear 'now', I'll change it for you right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.80,0:27:34.04,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,In that blue sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.68,0:27:37.24,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,looking up, the brilliant blue will take us away.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.81,0:27:39.31,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.88,0:27:42.56,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,yes, everything, I'll block out the distractions.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.56,0:27:45.52,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,I'll even protect you from fate itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.16,0:27:51.72,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,I'll support you; you have a place here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.52,0:27:53.48,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Don't you ever lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.40,0:28:12.56,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Love Live! Superstar!! Yuigaoka Girls' Lunchtime Broadcasting Station, Lieraji.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.56,0:28:13.06,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.00,0:28:19.00,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,News from Love Live! Superstar!!.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.24,0:28:21.42,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"This is music information."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.42,0:28:23.64,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"On Wednesday, July 8th, the release of the"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.64,0:28:27.24,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"'Liella! to Musubu Project' mini-album has been confirmed."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.24,0:28:34.82,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"We'll be releasing five versions: Original, Photo, Team Kids, Team Sports, and Team Green."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.82,0:28:41.94,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"The Original, Team Kids, Team Sports, and Team Green versions feature new illustrations,"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.94,0:28:45.26,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"while the Photo version uses new photos of the cast."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.26,0:28:52.44,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"It'll include four songs, including one new group track, plus off-vocal versions for a total of eight."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.44,0:28:56.76,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"As a first-press bonus, the Original, Team Kids,"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.76,0:29:00.44,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Team Sports, and Team Green versions will include member stickers."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.44,0:29:02.96,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"The Photo version will include print-club style stickers."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.56,0:29:08.10,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"All versions will also include advance lottery application tickets for the Love Live! Series 15th Anniversary Love Live! Fes"
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.10,0:29:11.60,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"and Love Live! Superstar!!."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.36,0:29:14.76,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Furthermore, as a bundle purchase bonus, we'll be giving away"
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.76,0:29:16.62,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"a Liella! sticker book."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.62,0:29:17.96,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Don't forget to pre-order.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.50,0:29:19.00,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,To celebrate the release of the
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.00,0:29:24.20,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"'Liella! to Musubu Project' mini-album, we've decided to hold handover events."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.72,0:29:29.20,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"The dates are Friday, October 2nd, and Friday, October 9th."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.72,0:29:31.20,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Those who pre-order or purchase the 'Liella! to Musubu Project' mini-album"
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.20,0:29:38.40,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"at participating stores will be entered into a lottery to be invited to the handover event."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.40,0:29:45.24,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"The cast members will vary by date, so please check the application requirements before applying."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.76,0:29:49.80,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Check the Love Live! Superstar!! official website for more details."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.68,0:29:53.83,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Next is news from the Love Live! Series Official Card Game."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.83,0:29:54.48,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,The 'Start Deck: Love Live! Superstar!!',
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.48,0:30:02.78,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"which only features Liella! members and songs, will be released on Saturday, May 30th."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.78,0:30:08.68,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"This product will include a special rarity called 'Secret Serial' with a serial number."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.20,0:30:13.88,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Each numbered card is a super-luxurious item, the only one of its kind in the world."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.44,0:30:24.60,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"The Start Deck has everything you need to play Loveca right away, so even if you've never played before, please grab one and get started."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.36,0:30:32.36,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Latest info will be posted on the Love Live! official site and X, so keep an eye out."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.08,0:30:34.22,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Here is some appearance information."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.22,0:30:35.84,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Starting April 1st, Liella!'s"
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.84,0:30:36.68,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"'ChuChu Liella!'"
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.68,0:30:38.64,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Season 2 will begin on Nippon TV."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.16,0:30:43.04,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Haishin-san No. 3 will continue as the program MC from Season 1."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.68,0:30:48.86,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Catch-up streaming will be available on TVer and NTV Tada after the broadcast."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.86,0:30:50.04,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Don't forget to check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.64,0:30:54.96,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Additionally, to commemorate the broadcast, the live event 'Love Live! Superstar!! Liella!'s
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.96,0:30:55.88,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,ChuChu Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.88,0:31:02.34,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"2026' will be held at LaLa arena TOKYO-BAY on August 1st and 2nd."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.34,0:31:10.02,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Official 2nd lottery applications are currently open on Ticket Pia until 11:59 PM on Sunday, April 5th."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.02,0:31:11.80,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Please check this out as well."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.44,0:31:16.74,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"For details on all the information announced today, please check the official Liella!"
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.74,0:31:21.56,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"X account and the Love Live! Superstar!! official website."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.56,0:31:23.32,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"That's all for the announcements."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.16,0:31:35.68,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Love Live! Superstar!! Yuigaoka Girls' Lunchtime Broadcasting Station, Lieraji."
Comment: 0,0:31:35.68,0:31:38.46,Date Sayuri,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Closing ===
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.68,0:31:38.46,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It's almost time to say goodbye to the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.46,0:31:41.00,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Here is some information about our upcoming broadcasts."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.00,0:31:51.24,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Episode 266, scheduled for Tuesday, March 31st, will also feature Yabushima Akane, the voice of Yoneme Mei."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.24,0:32:02.22,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"And for Episode 267 on Tuesday, April 7th, we'll have Ohkuma Wakana, the voice of Wakana Kinako, joining the Toma-Kano-Shiki trio."
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.22,0:32:04.44,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"We're looking forward to your messages!"
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.44,0:32:07.24,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"So, how did you enjoy today's broadcast?"
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.80,0:32:08.76,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.44,0:32:10.16,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.84,0:32:11.80,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Ding ding ding!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.64,0:32:13.48,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,What? Is it always like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.89,0:32:15.39,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Ding ding ding!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.12,0:32:19.08,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Sakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.08,0:32:19.96,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Oh no, oh no, oh no, oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.96,0:32:21.84,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Saku... Sakura, you really surprised me just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.84,0:32:23.92,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I didn't expect you to switch to this side.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.92,0:32:26.88,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I was thinking, "When did Sakura become like this?"
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.88,0:32:27.68,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,They're worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.52,0:32:33.80,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I couldn't think of a comeback, so I figured I'd just join in on the fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.96,0:32:32.46,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,That's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.00,0:32:34.88,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yes, wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.88,0:32:37.18,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yabushima looked so confused just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.18,0:32:38.80,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Saku... Sakura, they're worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.88,0:32:41.92,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Being pitied is the most embarrassing thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.96,0:32:44.26,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Anyway, how was it today?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.26,0:32:49.34,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Well, I got to talk about my impressions in such detail...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.34,0:32:51.16,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I mean, I talked quite a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.76,0:32:52.66,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Is that really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.66,0:32:53.92,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you so much."
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.92,0:32:55.08,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Everyone wanted to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.76,0:32:57.99,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,We'll talk more next week too.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.99,0:32:58.56,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.56,0:33:02.34,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah. I wonder how long we're allowed to keep talking about "7."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.34,0:33:05.62,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,We're planning to keep this going for about three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.62,0:33:06.78,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Roughly, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.78,0:33:09.32,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,We'll do it until we've gone through every song.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.92,0:33:08.84,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Oh, then let's do every single song.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.52,0:33:10.80,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,We won't be able to do the unit lives anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.56,0:33:12.26,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I don't know about that."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.26,0:33:12.84,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"We're running over!"
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.84,0:33:13.86,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"We're running over! We're running over!"
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.60,0:33:19.32,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Well then, that's all for this episode of Love Live! Superstar!! Yuigaoka Girls' Lunchtime Broadcast Station: Lieraji!"
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.32,0:33:20.18,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,That's all for this episode of "Lieraji."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.18,0:33:22.36,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Your hosts were Date Sayuri, the voice of Shibuya Kanon,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.36,0:33:24.60,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Sakakura Sakura, the voice of Onitsuka Tomari,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.60,0:33:26.80,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"and Yabushima Akane, the voice of Yoneme Mei."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.40,0:33:27.96,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.72,0:33:36.64,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,In the breathtaking twilight, I heard you say "see you."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.56,0:33:39.20,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,"The Gentle Breeze and You."
